Package: rin
Type: Package
Title: RStudio Interface to the 'rin' R Package Manager
Version: 0.1.1
Authors@R: person("Ajinkya", "Patil", email = "pajinkya66@gmail.com",
    role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A thin wrapper around the 'rin' command-line R package manager,
    letting you install, audit, resolve and manage project-local
    environments from inside R and RStudio. It locates the 'rin' binary
    (even when it is not on the GUI session's PATH), streams the binary's
    live output to the R console, and refreshes the library search path so
    that freshly installed packages are usable immediately, without
    restarting the session.
